mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我無野講 <br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我有權拍片紀錄 保障自己<br />\n我要搵律師<br />\n我要警誡紀錄 否則唔去錄影會面<br />\n我唔舒服要去醫院<br />\n我要毛毯"},{"pid":"c40594f261c084bf4b876c6aa29dfeaa4afa62c0","tid":1295094,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}